{"tid":2081609,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駐港公署：《中英聯合聲明》的核心與港人治港、高度自治無關","createTime":"2020-06-27T10:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T11:16:05.000Z","uid":7542,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b80d022244d14a88ec484e4e0b680c615d83a92f","tid":2081609,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署表示，堅決反對美國宣布對中方官員採取簽證限制措施，<span style=\"color: red;\">敦促美方立即糾正錯誤，停止干預香港事務和中國内政的霸凌行徑</span>，否則必將遭到中方有力回擊。發言人指出，美方誣衊中國政府破壞香港高度自治，完全是顛倒黑白、自欺欺人。國安立法是堅持和完善一國兩制方針的重大舉措，以及推動香港走出亂局困境、實現長治久安的根本之策，形容隨著相關立法順利推進，香港社會正迎來驅散陰霾再出發的曙光。發言人重申，堅決反對美方拿《中英聯合聲明》做幌子干預香港事務。<span style=\"color: red;\">《聯合聲明》的核心是中國對香港恢復行使主權</span>，隨著1997年7月1日香港回歸中國，包括美、英在內的外國對中國香港無主權、無治權、無監督權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=17ff0af4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a><br />\n<br />\n剪片時聽了超過十次，但每次都起哂雞皮，去到最後都係忍唔住喊。<br />\n<br />\n提醒自己，你不是孤單的。<br />\n亦不要讓其他抗爭者感到孤單。"},{"pid":"4f76b146cd901a415a390847a0eb55d0ba78085d","tid":2081609,"uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"汁：<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534441-20200627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534441-20200627.htm&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=6b60f1d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534441-20200627.htm&h=65758f74\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534441-20200627.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c643a8138da28cf07f1eeb75f79052dd9fd62e7e","tid":2081609,"uid":250775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10